A rowdy drinker who was asked to leave a bar came back and threw beer bottles filled with gasoline at its owner.

Christopher Colosimo, 42, was asked to leave the Cagney's Saloon in Davie, Florida, on Monday morning.

The man returned with a makeshift petrol bomb in two bottles - sometimes referred to as a Molotov cocktail.

