Colosimo, of Fort Lauderdale, Florida, set light to his creations before hurling them at the bar's owner, who was outside at the time.

The owner and none of those drinking inside were injured.

Davie Police Captain Dale Engle told the Orlando Sentinel: 'They kick him out, he gets upset, he leaves. He comes back with two beer bottles filled with gasoline.'

